    "prompt": "<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows three identical blocks labeled A, B, and C. Block A has a temperature of 300 kelvin. Block B has a temperature of 250 kelvin. Block C has a temperature 450 kelvin. The blocks are in a row (from left to right, A, B, and C) and are touching. The blocks are insulated from their environment.\" src=\"/images/157f7bb97ed954334d0b386824f6fa03.svg\"></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Blocks <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"A\"><math alttext=\"A\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">A</mi></math></span></span>, <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"B\"><math alttext=\"B\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">B</mi></math></span></span>, and <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"C\"><math alttext=\"C\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">C</mi></math></span></span> are made of the same material, and have identical sizes, shapes, and masses. Blocks <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"A\"><math alttext=\"A\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">A</mi></math></span></span>, <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"B\"><math alttext=\"B\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">B</mi></math></span></span>, and <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"C\"><math alttext=\"C\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">C</mi></math></span></span> are initially at temperatures of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"300 kelvin\"><math alttext=\"300 kelvin\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>300</mn><mspace width=\"0.2em\"></mspace><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">K</mi></math></span></span>, <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"250 kelvin\"><math alttext=\"250 kelvin\" display=\"inline\" o